    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_886361877458586656.png",
                "id": "talent63282",
                "key": "往生秘传枪法",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "往生秘传枪法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>本角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">彼岸蝶舞</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/786741b419f21d96999ca7832a738088_2732535655306593520.png",
                "id": "talent12343",
                "key": "蝶引来生",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "蝶引来生"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>，治疗自身2点。如果本角色生命值不多于6，则造成的伤害和治疗各+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/3fd894c657ed5975d54c71d665e6bcc9_1497914313316319829.png",
                "id": "talent36466",
                "key": "安神秘法",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "安神秘法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着火元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧</span>：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火元素伤害的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧烈焰</span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_6790807456862768892.png",
                "id": "talent7877",
                "key": "火元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">彼岸蝶舞</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>所附属角色造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>变为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>，且角色造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色进行重击时：</span>目标角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">血梅香</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">持续回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合结束阶段，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">重击</span></strong></p><p>我方开始行动前，如果元素骰总数为偶数，则进行的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「普通攻击」</span>将被视为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「重击」</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">血梅香</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>对所附属角色造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_7297012134276577916.png",
